# WordCloud     
params = {
    "width"  : 800,
    "height" : 600, 
    "max_words" : 400,
    "colormap"  : "magma", 
    "background_color" :"orange"
}

wordcolud_3 = WordCloud(**params)
wordcolud_3 = wordcolud_3.generate(text) 

save_img = 'img/wordcolud_constitution_3.png'
plt.figure(figsize=(24,16))
plt.imshow(wordcolud_3)
plt.axis('off')
plt.savefig(save_img)
